{"id":694930,"global_id":"Z2lkOi8vaGFja2Vyb25lL1JlcG9ydC82OTQ5MzA=","url":"https://hackerone.com/reports/694930","title":"[snekserve] Stored XSS via filenames HTML formatted","state":"Closed","substate":"resolved","severity_rating":"medium","readable_substate":"Resolved","created_at":"2019-09-14T17:59:43.837Z","submitted_at":"2019-09-14T17:59:43.837Z","is_member_of_team?":false,"is_organization_group_member?":false,"is_triager?":false,"reporter":{"disabled":false,"username":"mik317","url":"/mik317","profile_picture_urls":{"small":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/000/235/168/b1978368a15e57488f15b4f8aff454d3e3e98184_original.png/235acf2ba808c3a51a94888fb977392c26f8fb0ccf77a81a4546c5e4065c06f1"},"is_me?":false,"cleared":false,"verified":false,"hackerone_triager":false,"hacker_mediation":false},"team":{"id":23949,"url":"https://hackerone.com/nodejs-ecosystem","handle":"nodejs-ecosystem","profile_picture_urls":{"small":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/000/023/949/3ea3b2ae039a8f955a4a8fe65d99fe85dc817398_original./235acf2ba808c3a51a94888fb977392c26f8fb0ccf77a81a4546c5e4065c06f1","medium":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/000/023/949/3ea3b2ae039a8f955a4a8fe65d99fe85dc817398_original./3f1ab5c6a9b6dadada1e6c8121700b884388bd0a43471fee1897a38ce57d0b2c"},"permissions":[],"submission_state":"disabled","default_currency":"usd","awards_miles":false,"offers_bounties":true,"state":"public_mode","only_cleared_hackers":false,"pentest_feature_enabled?":false,"pentest_retesting_ends_at":null,"profile":{"name":"Node.js third-party modules","twitter_handle":"","website":"https://nodejs.org/en/security/","about":"This program was used to handle vulnerabilities in the Node.js ecosystem."}},"has_bounty?":false,"can_view_team":true,"can_view_report":true,"is_external_bug":false,"is_published":false,"is_participant":false,"has_collaborators":false,"submitted_by_team_member":false,"submitted_with_assistant":false,"stage":4,"public":true,"visibility":"full","cve_ids":[],"singular_disclosure_disabled":false,"disclosed_at":"2020-09-24T19:27:13.000Z","bug_reporter_agreed_on_going_public_at":null,"team_member_agreed_on_going_public_at":"2020-08-25T19:26:53.739Z","comments_closed?":false,"facebook_team?":false,"team_private?":false,"vulnerability_information":"I would like to report a `stored XSS` issue in the `snekserve` module.\nIt allows to `inject HTML/JS` code inside the `directory listing` :)\n\n# Module\n**module name:** `snekserve`\n**version:** `1.0.0`\n**npm page:** `https://www.npmjs.com/package/snekserve`\n\n## Module Description\n\u003e Assuming you would like to serve a static site, single page application or just a static file (no matter if on your device or on the local network), this package is just the right choice for you.\n\n## Module Stats\n[N/A] downloads in the last day\n[1] downloads in the last week\n[~20] downloads in the last month\n\n## Vulnerability Description\nThe filenames aren't checked correctly, leading to `stored XSS` inside the `directory listing` :)\n\n## Steps To Reproduce:\n1. Create a PoC file like this:\n\n```html\n\u003c!-- malicious.html --\u003e\n\u003cscript\u003ealert(document.domain)\u003c/script\u003e\n```\n2. Run the following commands:\n\n```bash\nnpm i snekserve -g # Installs the CLI version of the module\nmkdir '\u003ciframe src=..\\malicious.html\u003e' # Creates the malicious *HTML formatted* folder\nsnekserve # Starts the server\n# Open a browser and go on http://localhost:8080\n```\n3. Opening the server initialized (on `localhost:8080`), you'll see the `alert(document.domain)` code executed :) {F582927}\n\n## Patch\n\u003e Validate the filenames before put them in the `directory listing`\n\n## Supporting Material/References:\n- [OPERATING SYSTEM VERSION]: Kali Linux\n- [NODEJS VERSION]: 10.16.3\n- [NPM VERSION]: 6.0.9\n\n# Wrap up\n- I contacted the maintainer to let them know: [N] \n- I opened an issue in the related repository: [N]\n\n## Impact\n\n`Stored XSS` on `snekserve` via `filename HTML injection`","weakness":{"id":62,"name":"Cross-site Scripting (XSS) - Stored"},"original_report_id":null,"original_report_url":null,"attachments":[{"id":582927,"file_name":"Screenshot_from_2019-09-14_17-56-48.png","expiring_url":"https://hackerone-us-west-2-production-attachments.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/mJwuDsw2Gsgywa72VnWx1xvB?response-content-disposition=attachment%3B%20filename%3D%22Screenshot_from_2019-09-14_17-56-48.png%22%3B%20filename%2A%3DUTF-8%27%27Screenshot_from_2019-09-14_17-56-48.png\u0026response-content-type=image%2Fpng\u0026X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256\u0026X-Amz-Credential=ASIAQGK6FURQ2USB7TJJ%2F20260429%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request\u0026X-Amz-Date=20260429T084555Z\u0026X-Amz-Expires=3600\u0026X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjECkaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJHMEUCIHDPJM%2F35syzy5fU%2B%2FnamB6i%2BwZYFti3l8zkfM4NyA%2BzAiEAp05QK3iAGMOwtaN4AnHYcdakFkvtu100pLUoyZuFOhAquwUI8f%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2FARADGgwwMTM2MTkyNzQ4NDkiDHdoZ3Qlyvk6qGGmYCqPBWW6XffjLQkZ2GRH%2Bc2bgCybAf%2BjROEWgjSexmWPQxhORppA94Z%2BQdocqzZhNoD2kzvq1YnffhxBpO6r3PiMZTyU%2FgFFKvABslQnPk%2BkXJu91fN3O4hEofZYfcwJVwePgOsTIVPuveUnzFfBoIRbjmlJZVgGgeK03L8ugC5hE2yHb4CMrB3thcROu44krUKIJIeCeJo3LBzFSRYQmO2cQC5JUY9A2Pf3ldBjxELeYtczEnaAQtZ9KDPheu8HCcCfKTpA79YvXM%2B2sEFZtwh1t096rHR1xGkRSGgnxPHj7IEezPfakjZqh7VqId5x%2BEH8nZdXn9MKqmOjQZ%2FY%2F%2Byw2uySmsOgmchxPJUrZ%2B4FwGGC4Itba8Y9uZ%2BbufFdYLFbmYwBl577dIwwQlx%2FohV9q%2BpD6cwjxrddWT7N7xNeAFrj3COFrUl9rtQYEZ10Mn5mKBaDHG6c%2FSa6%2FDAnBis3c8VEu1PFfhjXc3tVHo7wswn5HxOGmskGPzoxR8o1HfFQT%2B6eBC7Oldas38HQfziojUQHciIyQLB0rH0mFlnvKU%2FGaA42V%2Bauu9Tk7xBtut2Iy9IJXHaFDzwI5QS%2BlT8q5jAFyyDealPqad%2FK2j%2BT9Lu6FZYDhuLO7trmmOizM0gsWHcw3mjwRigDcuaZetU%2BE3tnnRs1%2BZOPEMqVlMNE4c9IZO4fn1a2BIHTcHfjKUzFAw68%2FPLvYmb9f2IfrYHehbwaDlYb4%2BqjmuX0y3vC%2F0AiYI60VWpITtsO9QPaTLbxNxFWbE4kMX4SitVqa1Ovjf4vLz5%2FKnTqcjzslZv9FX1ezKlmgsJ4u9RU%2FmOcYnMxAxdu56wLmqY%2FX%2FnwXOp4Oqxn55FdWOz%2BXemN6%2F3JM3Aw2%2F7GzwY6sQGB